{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8482f04cbd","title":"中共中央关于增调粮食支援京、津、沪和东北三省的通知","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"181be90560","index":0,"year":1958,"month":8,"day":5,"articleId":"8482f04cbd"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"16d6f1821a","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于增调粮食支援京、津、沪和东北三省的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"8482f04cbd"},{"id":"d843743247","type":"appellation","text":"上海局，各省、区、市委，抄粮食部：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"8482f04cbd"},{"id":"3bb45a721c","type":"paragraph","text":"今年夏粮比去年增产将近70％。小麦、早稻丰收的地方，粮食情况缓和，库存增加。据粮食部报告，现在京、津、沪三市和辽宁、吉林、黑龙江三省的粮食库存，比上年同期减少了15亿多斤，接不上新粮，急需增加调入粮食9亿4千万斤。为此，希望南方夏粮丰收的省、区予以支援。增调粮食计划，由粮食部加以安排。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"8482f04cbd"},{"id":"362bc97293","type":"paragraph","text":"由于目前农村劳动力紧张，希调出粮食的省、区，适当安排劳动力，使调出的粮食能够及时运出来。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"8482f04cbd"},{"id":"2614726057","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央1958年8月5日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"8482f04cbd"}],"page":{"id":"286e4eae9e","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"8482f04cbd","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}